No. 10-453. Apotex, Inc., Petitioner v. Kathleen Sebelius, Secretary of Health and Human Services, et al. 562 U.S. 1194, 131 S. Ct. 1000,

178 L. Ed. 2d 854,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 696. January 18, 2011.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit denied.

Justice Kagan took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 384 Fed. Appx. 4.
